RSVP: Benita: 07066444319 or @thegoodtimegang_ IJE (Design Explore)- La Campagne Tropicana Beach Resort Do you need a break from the normal that you know? Do you want to dip yourself in the beauty and experiences that only nature can offer? Do you want to see new places, meet new people, and create long-lasting memories? Come on a tour and an exploration of La Campagne Tropicana in this first Ije (Design Explore) series. Explore the mangrove forest and watch a wide variety of tropical flora and fauna that include snake trees, mangroves, various species of epiphytes, monkeys, squirrels, bats, and various species of birds such as kingfishers, seahawks, egrets and ducks. Go fishing in the lagoon or do nothing but relax sandwiched in between the warm sands on the beach. And bask in the beauty of African décor. There is always a lot of adventures out there waiting for us to live them. Date: Saturday, May 1, 2021.
